- The function retrieves a pointer `map` using `rcu_dereference(kvm->arch.apic_map)` — this is a shared resource accessed under RCU locking.
- It then calls `kvm_apic_map_get_dest_lapic(..., &dst, ...)` which populates `dst`, a pointer to an array of `struct kvm_lapic *`.
